text: Sébastien Tayac (born 4 December 1975) is a French gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Nice
